data.description: ** Seller is offering up to a $10,000 closing credit to the buyer with an acceptable offer** Check out this stunning luxury living and investment potential 6-bedroom, 6-bath home located in the heart of Central Florida's most coveted resort community, Champions Gate. This FULLY FURNISHED, turn-key home comes complete with bookings currently in place. It is situated in one of the phases that allow for owner occupancy, short-term rental, or longterm rental – offering many possibilities. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a spacious open floorplan that seamlessly integrates the living area, kitchen, and dining spaces. Stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a large island make the kitchen a chef's delight. With six beautifully appointed bedrooms, including two master suites, guests can enjoy privacy and comfort during their stay. Step into your private screened lanai with a refreshing SOUTH-FACING pool. Soak up the Florida sun on the loungers, relax in the shade, or play a ping pong. Outdoor seating is ideal for enjoying the beautiful weather. The garage has been transformed into a game room, featuring billiard and air hockey tables - perfect for keeping guests of all ages entertained. Champions Gate resort offers many amenities, including a heated pool, spa, water slides, volleyball and tennis courts, fitness center, bar, game room, fitness center, cinema, 24-hour gated community, and much more! HOA fees include Cable TV, Internet, ground and yard maintenance, trash pickup, Clubhouse, and amenities, and is within minutes to I-4, restaurants, shopping, grocery stores, gas stations, Orlando theme parks and more. Existing bookings can convey should you choose to retain the current property manager. Don't miss this exceptional opportunity to own your beautiful home in Champions Gate. Schedule a showing TODAY and experience the pinnacle of comfort, convenience, and investment potential in beautiful Central Florida. Don't forget to check out the pictures and 3D tour!
